Weet Smart helps you control your Weet Smart devices. You can simply ask Alexa to control your smart home device.

Please follow the steps below to connect your Weet Smart products to Alexa:
(1). Download our "Weet Smart" app on the Android or iOS app store
(2). Create an account on our "Weet Smart" app
(3). You need to have some Weet Smart devices, e.g Smart Bulb, Smart Socket, Camera, Smart Vacuum;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Weet Smart" app and change the appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Weet Smart" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from Android, iOS, or Amazon app store;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Weet Smart" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Weet Smart", and you'll be navigated to the login page;
(9). Enter your Weet Smart account’s username and password, you'll be redirected to the success page;
(10). Now, your setup is now complete.

You can now enjoy voice control on your home devices. For example;
“Alexa, turn on the bedroom light.”
“Alexa, turn off the bedroom light.”
“Alexa set the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, brighten the bedroom light to 50%.”
“Alexa, dim the bedroom light to 50%.”
"Alexa set bedroom light to green."
"Alexa, set bedroom light to warm white."
